      "text": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12.0pt;\">A public health officer is attending a workshop on disaster preparedness. The facilitator presents various scenarios to the group for classification. Which of the following would not be considered a natural disaster?</span></p>",
      "unique_key": "Q6097882",
      "question_audio": null,
      "question_video": null,
      "map_id": 34724,
      "difficulty_level": "beginner",
      "subjects_id": [
        7
      ],
      "solution": "<p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><strong>Ans. C. Radiological Disaster</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><strong>Option C.</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><strong>Radiological disasters&nbsp;</strong>are <strong>not</strong> classified as <strong>natural disasters</strong> because they involve the release of <strong>radioactive substances or radiation</strong>, often due to human activities such as <strong>nuclear accidents </strong>or the <strong>improper handling</strong> of <strong>radioactive materials Example</strong>. <strong>Chernobyl Tragedy (1986)</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><strong><u>Explanation:</u></strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><strong>Option A. Meteorological Disasters:</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Incorrect,</strong> as these are caused by <strong>climatic or weather</strong>-<strong>related phenomena</strong> and are considered <strong>natural disasters.</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><strong>Option B. Geophysical Disasters:</strong>&nbsp;<strong>Incorrect</strong> because they result from <strong>geological</strong> processes of the Earth, like <strong>earthquakes and volcanoes</strong> and are <strong>natural disasters</strong>.</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><strong>Option D. Biological Disasters:&nbsp;Incorrect&nbsp;</strong>as they are caused by <strong>biological hazards</strong> like <strong>pandemics</strong> or <strong>infestations</strong> and are considered <strong>natural disasters.</strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><strong><u>Educational Objective:</u></strong></span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\">Classification of Disasters</span></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><img src=\"https://cerebellum-web-static.s3.amazonaws.com/media/public/images/2024/08/02/screenshot-2024-08-02-113007.png\" alt=\"\" width=\"1000\" height=\"698\"></p><p>&nbsp;</p><p><span style=\"font-size:12pt;\"><strong>Reference: Park 26<sup>th</sup> ed p 889</strong></span></p>",
